529
00:39:37,520 --> 00:39:41,670
<i>Dylan said to say, erm, "Baby Bunting".</i>

530
00:39:41,690 --> 00:39:43,540
<i>He said that's what you call him.</i>

531
00:39:43,560 --> 00:39:47,130
